  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 14: Allerheiligen Waterfalls &amp; Renchtal</name>
    <desc>A stunning loop combining the atmospheric ruins of Allerheiligen monastery, its cascading waterfalls, and the beautiful Renchtal—finished off with a stretch of the legendary B500.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
  <wpt lat="49.322000" lon="8.548000">
